snippet.title: Celebrities Apologizing For Defending Amber Heard! (Elon Musk, Jason Momoa, etc.)
snippet.description:
Celebrities Like Jason Momoa & Elon Musk Apologize For Defending Amber Heard!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

In July 2020, during his closing speech at Johnny Depp's libel suit against the British tabloid The Sun, Johnny's lawyer David Sherbourne called Amber Heard a compulsive liar with a propensity to abuse, he said “He has never hit a woman in his entire life period full stop nada” and explained how Amber was the one who physically attacked Johnny on multiple occasions. 

Since then several celebrities have chimed in with their statements supporting Johnny and accused Amber of being a liar and even some celebrities that supported Amber have switched sides to Johnny and apologized for taking her side in the first place! Which begs the question, who were these celebrities and what did they say to defend Amber which they are now sorry for?

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #ElonMusk
